# Portfolio Configuration Reference Guide

This file is a quick reference for all configuration options in the `/config` folder.  
**Note:** This file does NOT affect your site - it's just documentation for your reference!

---

## ğŸ“‹ Commission Status

**File:** `config/commission-status.json`

**What it does:** Controls the commission status display at the top of the About Me section.

**Available Options:**

| Status Value | Display Text | Color | When to Use |
|-------------|--------------|-------|-------------|
| `"open"` | OPEN | ğŸŸ¢ Green | Actively accepting new commissions |
| `"closed"` | CLOSED | ğŸ”´ Red | Not accepting any commissions right now |
| `"full"` | FULL | ğŸŸ¡ Yellow | Commission slots are all filled |
| `"waitlist"` | WAITLIST | ğŸ”µ Blue | Not taking new commissions but accepting waitlist |
| `"paused"` | PAUSED | ğŸŸ£ Purple | Temporarily paused (vacation, break, etc.) |
| `"2 slots"` | 2 SLOTS | ğŸŸ¢ Green | Showing specific number of available slots |
| `"3 slots"` | 3 SLOTS | ğŸŸ¢ Green | Works with any number + "slots" |
| `"custom text"` | CUSTOM TEXT | âšª White | Any other text you want (default white) |

**Example Usage:**
```json
{
  "status": "open"
}
```

**How to Change:**
1. Go to `config/commission-status.json` on GitHub
2. Click the pencil icon (Edit)
3. Change the status value
4. Commit changes
5. Wait 1-2 minutes for site to update

