## ğŸ“ Notes

- All files in `/config` should be valid JSON format
- Changes take 1-2 minutes to appear on the live site
- Always test after making changes
- Keep backups of your config files before major changes
- File names are case-sensitive!

---

## ğŸ†˜ Troubleshooting

**Status not updating?**
- Check if file name is exactly `commission-status.json`
- Verify JSON format is valid (use jsonlint.com)
- Wait 2-3 minutes for GitHub Pages to rebuild
- Hard refresh your browser (Ctrl+Shift+R)

**Color not showing?**
- Make sure status value is lowercase
- Check spelling matches exactly (e.g., "closed" not "Closed")
- For custom status, it will default to white

